{"tid":605281,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"前加泰主席普伊格蒙特　在德國被捕","createTime":"2018-03-25T13:30:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-26T10:23:37.000Z","uid":53379,"like":22,"dislike":44,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"d5fcc41034c533c5ef3b5f9d560bdf5c3a0b4410","tid":605281,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T13:30:28.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">前加泰主席普伊格蒙特　在德國被捕</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180325/s00005/a23033ebbe1db316d5a1b0f7a15f8c16.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180325%2Fs00005%2Fa23033ebbe1db316d5a1b0f7a15f8c16.jpg&h=fba5c461&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n前加泰隆尼亞自治政府主席普伊格蒙特（Carles Puigdemont），周日（25日）早上在德國及丹麥接壤邊境地區，被德國警方帶走拘留。<br />\n<br />\n西班牙最高法院上周五（23日）宣布，決定以謀反罪名，起訴普伊格蒙特等13名爭取加泰獨立的領袖，並發出歐洲逮捕令。如果罪名成立，各人最高可被判監25年。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n普伊格蒙特去年10月底開始流亡比利時，上周四抵達芬蘭與當地議員會面。有議員透露，普氏在西班牙法院發出拘捕令當晚已離境。其代表律師則說，普伊格蒙特原打算返回比利時，但從丹麥過境德國時被捕，目前在一間警局內拘留。<br />\n<br />\n（法新社）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180325/s00005/1521979246373\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180325%2Fs00005%2F1521979246373&d=MaY%2BkJneBDezoLvWMdCsw%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=8a2f6b5d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180325%2Fs00005%2F1521979246373&h=8589b160\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180325/s00005/1521979246373</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8e32f5cb6b98a3d53b7f4e1c6178f27fee792cf","tid":605281,"uid":66324,"like":39,"dislike":1,"score":38,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T13:51:42.000Z","msg":"成班左膠搬龍門，醜態百出<br />\n抵比班難民搞死"},{"pid":"53cdc1f49823a914b88c32d3b7b9b416a5ff897b","tid":605281,"uid":47359,"